show.description: Divorce ka Punchanama plunges into the tumultuous life of Ishaan Malhotra. His engagement shatters when his fiancée, Alisha Kamra, mistakenly believes his pregnant aunt, Jahnvi Malhotra, is his mistress. This initial misunderstanding quickly spirals into a dark and intricate narrative of deceit, aggression, and shocking secrets
